PrecisRe-appointment of JACQUES LAPOMMERAY, of Candiac, Quebec, and JOSÉ TSHISUNGU WA TSHISUNGU, of Montreal, Quebec, as full-time members of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Montreal Regional Office), to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years, effective January 19, 2001.
